{"type":null,"faqId":40422,"title":"路由器经常掉线，不稳定，怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p7{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p8{margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;color:#00a0e9;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n.s4{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.td1{width:1.7222222in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid darkgray;border-top:thin solid darkgray;}\n.td2{width:1.7229167in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid darkgray;border-top:thin solid darkgray;}\n.t1{table-layout:fixed;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>路由器掉线的原因一般比较复杂。您可以按照以下步骤进行排查。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">检查一：确认WAN接口网线是否连接牢靠</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请查看路由器的蓝色网口（WAN接口）的网线是否存在接口松动、接触不良的情况，并尝试更换一根网线后重新检查。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">检查二：确认路由器是否为最新的软件版本</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以定期升级路由器的软件版本来提高路由器网络的稳定性。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><a name=\"OLE_LINK15\"><span>登录路由器</span><span>Web配置界面</span><span>。</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">更多功能 &gt; 路由器升级</span><span>“。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>在”</span><span class=\"s3\">在线升级</span><span>“区域框中单击”</span><span class=\"s3\">检测新版本</span><span>“检查路由器的是否为最新的软件版本。若有新的软件版本，请根据页面提示完成在线升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137235\" style=\"width:5.5125in;height:3.9819446in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">检查三：确认宽带服务商的网络是否稳定</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>去掉路由器，直接用网线连接电脑和因特网(如宽带猫、光猫) 。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137236\" style=\"width:3.3263888in;height:0.85555553in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">控制面板 &gt; 网络和共享中心 &gt; 设置新的连接或网络 &gt; 连接到 Internet</span><span>”。单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">下一步</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">宽带（PPPoE）</span><span>”，在“</span><span class=\"s3\">用户名</span><span>”和“</span><span class=\"s3\">密码</span><span>”中分别输入宽带服务商提供的宽带上网账号和密码。单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">连接</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137237\" style=\"width:5.513889in;height:4.3319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p  >\n<span>新建连接后，后续直接单击 “</span><span class=\"s3\">控制面板 &gt; 网络和共享中心 &gt;更改适配器设置</span><span>”，即可找到您刚刚创建宽带连接。双击“</span><span class=\"s3\">宽带连接</span><span>”图标，即可直接通过单台电脑验证是否可以通过单台电脑PPPoE拨号上网。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137238\" style=\"width:3.7243056in;height:3.6694446in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s4\">&gt;  </span><span>若单台电脑直接拨号上网，网路仍然出现掉线的情况，则说明宽带服务商出现故障，请及时致电您的宽带服务商。常见的宽带服务商电话如下，仅供参考。</span>\n</p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s3\">中国电信</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s3\">中国联通</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s3\">中国移动</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s3\">长城宽带</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>10000</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>10010</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>10086</span>\n</p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>95079</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"p8\"></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s4\">&gt;  </span><span>若单台电脑直接拨号上网，网路正常，则请在路由器掉线时候，保存系统调试信息，请联系华为客服800 830 8300（仅固话）或400 830 8300。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p8\">\n<span>保存系统调试信息方法：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>登录路由器Web配置界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">更多功能 &gt; 系统设置 &gt; 调试</span><span>“。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击”</span><span class=\"s3\">收集调试信息</span><span>“保存调试信息即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137239\" style=\"width:5.507639in;height:4.60625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5769","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":144